== Compilation ==

This project uses CMake to build the source code.

mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path
make
make install

== CMake command line options ==

- USE_DOUBLE=ON/OFF         Enable/disable double floating precision
- DISABLE_OPENMP=On/OFF     Enable/disable OpenMP support
- DISABLE_OPENGL=On/OFF     Enable/disable OpenGL support

== Dependencies ==

- OpenCL >= 1.2 (required)
- libmath (required)
- OpenMP (optional)
- OpenGL & GLUT (optional)
